metadata.name: Pure Conviction
metadata.description:
It's been a difficult journey so far, dealt with so much it has weakened me. Thankfully, I am a believer that no suffering lasts forever, I just need to buckle down and be prepared.  
This is my outlook on taking this year by storm. Watch out for me, I won't be hard to find.



Artist: ArtofNuel (Emmanuel Inua)  
Medium: Digital Painting (Procreate)  
Dimensions: 12 by 15 inches (3600px by 4500px), 300ppi.  
Year: January 2023.
